title: Hopare, Kashink & NIARK1 x Converse Get Loud: Paris
description:
Parisian artists Hopare, Kashink and NIARK1 each took to the metro to add their own #GetLoud twist to our billboards.

Track: Droog "On My Way to Work"

Recording made with authorization of Metrobus, Paris.
